Privacy Policy for Pomodoro Plus App

At Pomodoro Plus, we prioritize the privacy and security of our users. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our app.

Information Collection and Usage:

We do not collect any personal information from our users. Pomodoro Plus does not require you to create an account or provide any personal details. We do not store, share, or transmit any user data to third parties.

Notification Permissions:

Pomodoro Plus may request permission to send notifications to provide you with timely reminders for your work sessions and breaks. We do not use notifications for any other purpose, and we do not collect or store any user-specific data related to notifications.

Third-Party Services:

Pomodoro Plus does not integrate or utilize any third-party services or frameworks that may collect your personal information. We maintain strict control over the app's functionality and ensure that your privacy is safeguarded.

Data Security:

We take appropriate measures to protect the security of your information and prevent unauthorized access or disclosure. However, please note that no method of data transmission or storage is entirely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Changes to the Privacy Policy:

We reserve the right to modify or update this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the updated policy within the app. We recommend reviewing this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about how we handle your information.

Contact Us:

If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding our app or privacy practices, please contact us at mustafa@altinisik.net. We will be happy to assist you and address any inquiries you may have.

By using Pomodoro Plus, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
